7 An Act relating to the Oklahoma State Bureau of
Investigation; making an appropriation; stating
8 purpose; providing an effective date; and declaring
an emergency.
9
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the Cyber Crime and
13 Fraud Unit Fund, established in Enrolled Senate Bill No. 1859 of the
14 2nd Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature, from any monies not
15 otherwise appropriated from the General Revenue Fund of the State
16 Treasury for the fiscal year ending June 30, 2027, the sum of One
17 Million Five Hundred Thousand Dollars ($1,500,000.00) or so much
18 thereof as may be necessary for the Oklahoma State Bureau of
19 Investigation to carry out the provisions of Enrolled Senate Bill
20 No. 1859 of the 2nd Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature.
21 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
22 SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
23 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
24
